            <title>小米卢伟冰：Redmi 研发首款产品不达标，4000 万“打了水漂”</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/735/931.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/735/931.htm</guid>
